title: Camelia Lupașcu
text: Camelia Gabriela Lupașcu (born 29 July 1986 in <a href="Dorohoi">Dorohoi</a>) is a Romanian rower. She finished 4th in the <a href="Rowing%20at%20the%202012%20Summer%20Olympics%26amp%3Bnbsp%3B%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20eight">eight</a> at the <a href="2012%20Summer%20Olympics">2012 Summer Olympics</a>.
